title: ARSUK Self Resetting Air Rifle Airgun Target for Precision Shooting Practice, Airsoft BB Guns Target Heavy-Duty Metal Frame to Withstand Repeated Shots, Suitable for calibers .177 & .22 Pellets
features: Precision Target Practice – Enhances accuracy with air rifles, BB, and pellet guns.
Self-Resetting Design – Hit the target, and it auto-resets for nonstop action.
Heavy-Duty Steel Build – Durable construction withstands repeated shots.
Weather-Resistant Coating – Perfect for outdoor use in all conditions.
Designed for .177 & .22 Caliber – Ideal for air rifles, BB, and pellet guns.
No Batteries or Power Needed – Fully mechanical for hassle-free shooting.
Great for Backyard Plinking – Fun and safe for recreational shooting.
Ideal for Indoor & Outdoor Use – Versatile setup for any shooting space.
Perfect for Skill Training – Improves aiming, timing, and accuracy.
Compact & Portable – Easy to transport and quick to set up anywhere.
description: Benefits - Versatility in Use: ARSUK Air Rifle Targets are designed for air rifles, air guns, and BB guns, ensuring a versatile shooting experience suitable for various firearms. - Dynamic Shooting Engagement: Elevate your marksmanship with moving targets, providing an interactive and challenging air rifle shooting experience. The dynamic nature of these targets adds excitement and unpredictability to your practice sessions. - Comprehensive Training: Enhance your skills with included air rifle knockdown accessories and equipment. These features create a holistic training environment, allowing you to refine your technique and improve overall shooting performance. - Durable Construction: Crafted from robust steel, these targets ensure durability and resilience during air rifle shooting. Built to withstand repeated use, they offer long-lasting performance, making them a reliable choice for extended training sessions. - Convenient Setup and Portability: With a compact design and a weight of 780 grams, these targets are easy to set up and transport. Enjoy the convenience of on-the-go shooting practice, whether indoors or outdoors. - Enhanced Visibility: Featuring a sleek black color and orange target paper, these targets not only provide a professional appearance but also enhance visibility. Specifications - Product Name: Shooting Targets - Materials: Steel - Package dimensions: 31 x 24.3 x 6.7 cm - Color: Black, Target Color: Orange Package Included: 1x Air Rifle Target
